{"tid":2510944,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"除咗寫信同旁聽，仲有其他嘢可以幫到在囚嘅手足⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯","createTime":"2021-04-30T13:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T13:54:49.000Z","uid":209603,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0ad154b9013d46cf49fe39e66ebf951afb32b001","tid":2510944,"uid":209603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbbJDbqTZ2rVPCotQAzwJ6cv9kHvcvg6w8rwziHLE2NFk?filename=pzZgnkY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpzZgnkY.jpg&h=cba8efbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【📕為在囚手足徵集16本書籍📙】<br />\n<br />\n燕子生命正聯同天水連線及抗爭點滴為在囚手足徵集以下16本書本：<br />\n<br />\n1. 活出意義來──從集中營說到存在主義（已徵得）<br />\n2. 覺醒公民（已徵得）<br />\n3. 讚！日文初學20堂課1：從五十音進擊日文<br />\n4. 邊聽邊寫！簡單快速日文入門<br />\n5. 初學日文的第一堂課: 用康乃爾筆記法學日文<br />\n6. 一定要幸福喔！自己學也行的手相占卜<br />\n7. 開運 姓名判斷事典―姓名判斷、命名、改名が自分でできる!<br />\n8. 祕密三部曲套書：《The Secret 祕密》<br />\n9. 警國論（已徵得）<br />\n10. 要決心忘記 我便記不起 （鄭梓靈）<br />\n11. 低端中國：黨、土地、農民工，與中國即將到來的經濟危機（已徵得）<br />\n12. 萬獸寓言（劉銳紹）（已徵得）<br />\n13. 技術分析攻略（林瑞芬）<br />\n14. 記得你是誰：哈佛的最後一課（已徵得）<br />\n15. 反修例風暴採訪戰場<br />\n16. 平凡的邪惡 - 漢娜顎蘭<br />\n<br />\n如閣下能捐出，請務必先聯絡我們<br />\nTelegram: @swallowlife<br />\nFacebook: @swallowlife<br />\nInstagram: @swallowlife.hk<br />\n<br />\n圍牆上的圖書館旨在為在囚手足搜集各類書本、推介各個範疇高質書本以及定期製作書單予在囚手足挑選書本，並希望創造一個平台予香港人交流及搜集高質的書本，裝備思想、提升水平，留有用之身以待將來。<br />\n<br />\n圍牆上的圖書館<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swallowlife.org/圍牆上的圖書館\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swallowlife.org%2F%E5%9C%8D%E7%89%86%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%96%E6%9B%B8%E9%A4%A8&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTyHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=c5ab00ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swallowlife.org/圍牆上的圖書館</a><br />\n<br />\n天水連線X抗爭點滴X燕子生命－寫信師計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swallowlife.org/intro-heartwithmate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swallowlife.org%2Fintro-heartwithmate&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTyHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=07a5e5d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swallowlife.org/intro-heartwithmate</a>"},{"pid":"a0159a0724fc6b7288e59b2542307f51538c553d","tid":2510944,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8884e5f3abd7f010b6f44e5a1323637e6c8c28bd","tid":2510944,"uid":281713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:35:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec6aff557923e7baf7291ccba19fc1a8ef6f056","tid":2510944,"uid":241804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5522730ae55876b1dce97fb216e672edfccbcb","tid":2510944,"uid":209603,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a0159a0724fc6b7288e59b2542307f51538c553d","tid":2510944,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推呀"},{"pid":"7b548343024354f05c65b1926241271cb9fdf749","tid":2510944,"uid":281713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0e7a91da9516f5b6153322abc881a22c6398c8","tid":2510944,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:35:16.000Z",